---
import MainLayout from '../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import TedaviDoktorlari from '../../../components/TedaviDoktorlari.astro'; 

// SEO Title and Description
const pageTitle = "All On 4 Implant Treatment | Same Day Fixed Teeth | Yuceler A+ Clinic";
const pageDescription = "All On 4 implant treatment for total edentulism in Silivri and Catalca. Get fixed, aesthetic, and reliable teeth on the same day with only 4 implants.";

---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle}>
  
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/images/all-on-four-banner.webp');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-klinik-koyu/95 via-klinik-koyu/60 to-transparent z-0"></div> 
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-klinik-yesil text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-4 tracking-widest uppercase">Same Day Fixed Teeth</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-2xl">
          Fast Solution for Edentulism: <br/><span class="text-klinik-yesil">All On 4 Implant</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed drop-shadow-lg">
          For our patients who have lost or are about to lose all their teeth, the opportunity to have fixed, aesthetic, and functional teeth on the same day with just 4 implants.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
        
        <div class="w-full lg:w-2/3 prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">What is the All On 4 Implant Technique?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>All On 4</strong> is a fast and highly reliable surgical procedure applied to completely edentulous patients or cases where all teeth need to be extracted. While traditional methods require 6 to 8 implants per jaw for a fixed prosthesis, the All On 4 technique allows for fixed teeth on the entire jaw using <strong>only 4 titanium implants</strong> placed at special angles.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            In this technique, 2 straight implants are placed in the anterior part of the jaw, and 2 angled implants are placed in the posterior parts to avoid anatomical spaces (sinus cavity and nerve canals). The biggest advantage is that your temporary fixed teeth are placed on the <strong>same day the surgery is performed.</strong> You never leave the clinic without teeth.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-l-4 border-klinik-yesil mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">What are the Advantages of All On 4 Treatment?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Same Day Fixed Teeth:</strong> You return home with fixed (non-removable) temporary teeth hours after surgery.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>No Need for Advanced Surgery:</strong> Due to angled placement, additional and costly procedures like bone grafting or sinus lifting are often unnecessary.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>High Comfort:</strong> Completely eliminates sores, speech disorders, and the gag reflex caused by removable dentures.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-klinik-yesil" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg> <strong>Economical:</strong> Since fewer implants are used, it is more cost-effective than traditional full-jaw implant treatments.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-6">How Does the All On 4 Treatment Process Work?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">3D Tomography and Digital Planning</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">First, your jawbone is scanned with 3D volumetric tomography. The areas and angles where implants will be placed are planned down to the millimeter in a computer environment. Your temporary teeth are prepared in advance by taking your measurements.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Surgical Procedure and Temporary Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Under local anesthesia (or sedation if desired), any remaining problematic teeth are extracted, and 4 implants are placed in the jaw in the same session. Immediately after surgery, your pre-prepared fixed temporary teeth are screwed onto the implants.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-klinik-koyu text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-2">Placement of Permanent Aesthetic Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">An average of 3 months is waited for the implants to fuse completely with the bone. At the end of this period, your temporary teeth are removed, and your permanent porcelain or zirconium teeth, designed to perfectly suit your face, are placed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 sticky top-32">
          <img src="/images/all-on-four-kutu.webp" alt="All On 4 Implant Treatment" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-t-2xl shadow-sm" />
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 p-8 rounded-b-2xl shadow-xl">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Get Rid of Palate Dentures</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6 text-sm">Find out your suitability for All On 4 treatment immediately with a free 3D tomography and expert examination.</p>
            
            <a href="https://wa.me/902124000013" target="_blank" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.031 21.033c-1.56 0-3.084-.42-4.42-1.216l-.317-.189-3.284.861.876-3.203-.207-.331a9.022 9.022 0 0 1-1.378-4.755C3.301 7.155 7.215 3.24 12.031 3.24c2.33 0 4.519.907 6.166 2.555 1.648 1.648 2.556 3.837 2.556 6.167 0 4.914-3.915 8.829-8.73 8.829z" /></svg>
              Ask Price via WhatsApp
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+902124000013" class="w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-klinik-koyu text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-black transition-colors">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
              Call Clinic: +90 212 400 00 13
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TedaviDoktorlari tedavi="all-on-four" />

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 pb-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-klinik-koyu mb-4">Frequently Asked <span class="text-klinik-yesil">Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">What our patients wonder most about All On 4 implant treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Is the All On 4 treatment a painful procedure?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">No, because the surgical procedure is performed entirely under local anesthesia, you will not feel any pain during the operation. Any slight sensitivity or swelling that may occur after the procedure is easily managed with routine painkillers recommended by our doctor.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Who can get All On 4 treatment?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">All individuals who experience total edentulism in their jawbone, do not want to use a removable palate prosthesis, and do not have any systemic disease that would prevent implant surgery can safely benefit from this treatment.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between font-bold text-lg text-klinik-koyu">
            Can I eat immediately with temporary teeth?
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">Yes, you can eat, but it is crucial for the success of the implant that you avoid hard foods and consume only soft foods recommended by your doctor during the first 3-month period, which is the fusion period of the implants with the bone (osseointegration). After your permanent teeth are fitted, you can comfortably eat whatever you want.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="bg-klinik-koyu text-white py-12 border-t-4 border-klinik-turuncu mt-auto">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-klinik-turuncu font-bold text-lg mb-3">Legal Notice</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          This website has been prepared solely for the purpose of informing patients, in full compliance with the Ministry of Health regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-left md:text-right">
        <p class="mb-2 text-white font-semibold">Dental Implant Clinic A Plus</p>
        <p class="mb-1">Call Center: <span class="text-klinik-turuncu">+90 212 400 00 13</span></p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg inline-block text-left border border-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-1 text-xs">Last Updated: <span class="text-white font-bold">21.02.2026</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs">Editor: <a href="mailto:info@dentalimplanttrakya.com" class="text-klinik-turuncu hover:underline">info@dentalimplanttrakya.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <div class="h-16 md:hidden block"></div>

</MainLayout>